\"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9937185154571927, \"rank\": 0.0059817200889192654, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Senator\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 172}, {\"ngram\": \"the ongoing 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kingibe said that despite a 74-88 quarter-final loss to the USA, D'Tigress' performance in the face of adversity represents Nigerians' collective unyielding spirit.\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kingibe\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"a 74-88 quarter-final loss\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"the USA, D'Tigress' performance\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"adversity\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"Nigerians' collective unyielding spirit\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your fearless and gallant performance in the face of adversity represents our collective unyielding spirit.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your fearless and gallant performance\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"adversity\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"our collective unyielding spirit\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your rise like phoenixes in the 4th quarter against the wealthiest and most heavily invested team was a master class in resilience,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your rise\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"phoenixes\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4th quarter\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"the wealthiest and most heavily invested team\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"a master class\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While celebrating the D'Tigress, Kingibe emphasized the importance of cultural heritage, citing the National Arts Theatre in Lagos as a symbol of the nation's rich history and creative expression.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"D'Tigress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Arts Theatre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\", \"score\": 0.9997120015888866, \"rank\": 0.00028808137814493153, \"text\": \"Lagos\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kingibe\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural heritage\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"a symbol\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's rich history\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"creative expression\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said, \\\"The National Arts Theatre in Lagos hosted FESTAC '77, one of Africa's largest art, culture, and music festivals, and every aspect of this iconic building should reflect that legacy.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Arts Theatre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\", \"score\": 0.9997120015888866, \"rank\": 0.00028808137814493153, \"text\": \"Lagos\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\"}, {\"begin\": 912, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FESTAC_77\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FESTAC '77\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FESTAC_77\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FESTAC_77\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Africa's largest art\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"music festivals\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"every aspect\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"this iconic building\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"that legacy\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the basement of the National Arts Theatre is a treasure trove of artistic expression worth billions of naira, with art pieces that showcase the diverse cultural heritage of our beloved nation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Arts Theatre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Arts_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"naira\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerian_naira\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the basement\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"a treasure trove\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic expression\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"art pieces\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"the diverse cultural heritage\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"our beloved nation\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The senator called on the creative economy and tourism sectors to document, preserve, and protect the artifacts for the unborn generation.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The senator\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the creative economy and tourism sectors\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"document\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"the artifacts\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"the unborn generation\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She, therefore, asked for all hands on deck to promote cultural heritage, support artists, and sports people, and unlock the full potential of the nation's creative economy.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all hands\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"deck\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural heritage\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"support artists\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"sports people\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the full potential\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's creative economy\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We owe it to ourselves, our children, and future generations to preserve and celebrate our rich cultural legacy, just as we celebrate the achievements of our sheroes.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our children\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"future generations\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"our rich cultural legacy\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the achievements\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"our sheroes\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, we can build a great future that honors our past and inspires our future,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great future\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"our past\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"our future\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: Super Eagles midfielder set for MLS switch Transfer: I have to google him - Frank Leboeuf worry over incoming Chelsea signing D'Tigress maintain 8th position in latest FIBA women's rankings FIBA WWCQ: D'Tigress star Macaulay named in All-Star team D'Tigress captain Ogoke retires from national team FG fulfils pledge to D'Tigress for winning 2025 FIBA Women's Afrobasket 2026 FIBA World Cup Qualifiers: D'Tigress rally to 101-84 victory over Philippines FIBA WWQ 2026: Gallant D'Tigress fall 77-60 to Korea Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Eagles\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://d